Kouri in Scynthia.  As Alastor took off, Hercules quickly strode up beside him. "A lioness?," He replied.  "Well, that sounds of Hera.  I know she keeps one as a familiar.  I have only seen her a couple times.  She is good at staying out of site." Herc's blue orbs looked around as he kept up w/ Alastor's pace. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#003366><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=alastorofancients>Alastor of Ancients</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 18<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(7/8/01 10:32 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=110.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://caspervandien.net/sleepyhollow/themovie/photos/images/indeximageov.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> The Hunt</span><hr size=1> &quot;She well trained.. She hasn't killed her or broke anything by the look of it only frightened her into fainting.. &quot; Having been a hunter most his life he stops slowly ducking into the the cover of the brush and taking Hercules with him. He is silent as he motions with his hand, then pointing a finger up the rockside at a cave. He can almost hear their the lion breathing in his mind. He takes a rock slowly tossing it up at the mouth of the cave letting it tumble down the rock face. To make it seem someone is trying to sneak in above them. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#336699><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uqueenhera.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Queen Hera</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Bronze Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 115<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(7/9/01 5:53 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=110.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> the prey</span><hr size=1> As Maia sleeps in the cave, the night begins to take the skies and lands outside.  The cry of a peacock is heard as the Queen of the Gods appears near the sleeping lover of Zeus.  The cries awake her to see Hera standing above her.<br>
&quot;You have done well, Sin,&quot; Hera spoke calmly.  &quot;But, below it seems you have been followed.&quot; She said this all with her eyes upon the prize. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#003366><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/ulionessofhera.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Lioness of Hera</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 15<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(7/9/01 5:58 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=110.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> intruders</span><hr size=1> With the appearance of Hera in the Cave of Lions, Sin quickly rises to her feet.  Already, the Great Lion had heard the sound and stood at the foot of the cave.  He let out a loud roar and his pride soon appeared.  This pride of lions was only about 5.  They had come to Canathus to be with Sin, when it was finally known where Hera had brought the familiar.<br>
&quot;We shall take care of them, My Queen,&quot; answered Sin, who quickly transformed into a lioness and stood near the other 4 lioness and the Lion.  They lifted their noses to the scent of the air.  There was nothing above them.  And Sin's golden eyes turned in the direction of the trackers.   <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#336699><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uqueenhera.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Queen Hera</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Bronze Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 116<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(7/9/01 6:03 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=110.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> the prize</span><hr size=1> &quot;So, Maia,&quot; Hera spoke with evil intent in her voice. &quot;It seems that you had decided to defy me still, by sleeping with my husband. How dare you!  Against the Queen of the Gods, as well!&quot;<br>
Hera's blue eyes turned from icy blue to peacock feathers and the cave trembled as she spoke. As if even the ground knew Hera's fury.  Rocks began to shake and transform behind Maia and then two formations began to twists and turn pulling from the wall.  The formations grabbed Maia's arms, pulling her to the wall and then holding her in almost chains.<br>
&quot;I think you should stay here with the Lions for awhile,&quot; she cackled. &quot;Don't you?  Maybe time with them, will teach you a lesson.&quot;<br>
Hera laughed and then dissappeared.  Leaving Maia at the mercy of the lions. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#003366><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/ulionessofhera.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Lioness of Hera</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 16<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(7/9/01 6:10 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=110.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> trackers</span><hr size=1> Just as the trackers could see the pride of now six lions, with the transformation of Sin, as they glanced again.  Only the male lion stood at the entrance of the cave.  Blended in with the grasses, five lioness moved without a sound seperate from each other.  Their muscles tense as the moved towards Alastor and Hercules.  Sin's eyes were on Hercules.  Nervous energy rushed thru her veins as she and two sisters now stalked Hercules.  The two others sights were heavy and set upon Alastor.<br>
Sculking low, Sin was only 10 feet now from the son of Zeus.  Her claws flexed and then she rushed towards him, pouncing ontop of his side.  The thrust pushing him to the ground as her two sisters ran to join her.  <br>
With Sin's attack, the other two lioness rushed at Alastor. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#336699><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=alastorofancients>Alastor of Ancients</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 19<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(7/9/01 11:01 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=110.topic&index=10>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://caspervandien.net/sleepyhollow/themovie/photos/images/indeximageov.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> The attack.</span><hr size=1> As the Lionesses attack he turns to greet them, his reactions only a fraction of a second faster than the attack. He sent out an arm pushing Hercules towards the rockside as he saw the attackers coming towards them. &quot;Save the girl..&quot; He said as he was tackled by one of the large hunters his sword raised to face it. The force of the attack knocked him down under it's massive weight as the long sword peirced it's hide, all the way through exposing it selve through the back. He locks eyes with the lioness as the bulk of the hunter pinning him under it. Then looks towards the others charging towards Hercules. Pushing the lioness from his body chainmail dripping with the crimson liquid. As with a quick jerk pulled the sword from the lioness as the other one came to attack him. Trained to keep his head on his shoulders he pulled a rope with three rocks tied to it from his pouch. He throws it, the rope spiralling through the air. Before hitting the other attacker's legs tripping it up and tightly coiling them together. He breathed deepily looking towards the other three lioness letting out a roar to get their attention. He truly was the animal of the battle feild. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#003366><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uherculestlj.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Hercules TLJ</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Hero</span><br>  Posts: 99<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(7/9/01 11:14 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=110.topic&index=11>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> the attack</span><hr size=1> Hercules fell from the pounce of Sin upon him. The lioness was heavy, but with Alastor's help and his own strength he was able to throw her off of his body.  Nodding to Alastor, Hercules ran to the mountain and scrambled up the cliff.  <br>
He was met by the Lion guarding the entrance.  &quot;Well, here we go again,&quot; he said. It was not the first time he had go hand to hand with a male lion.  Hercules rushed the Lion and grabbed him.  His strong hands gripping the hide as tight as he can and then pushing the lion off the side of the short cliff.<br>
Turning to Maia, he rushed over and quickly broke the cave's grasp.  &quot;We have to get you out of here now!,&quot; Hercules helped Maia out of the cave and then up the side of the mountain.  He glanced down at Alastor to see if he needed his help. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#336699><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=alastorofancients>Alastor of Ancients</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 20<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(7/9/01 11:23 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=110.topic&index=12>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://caspervandien.net/sleepyhollow/themovie/photos/images/indeximageov.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Retreat.</span><hr size=1> &quot;Go to Zeus's temple. They won't get you there, Travel all day and night don't stop for anything.. &quot; He shouts over his shoulder as he holds his sword forward starting to back up the rockside, keeping the lionesses infront of him at all time. He gets about halfway up the hill putting his foot on a large rock slanting out of the rockside. He forces it forward with a jerk starting a chain reaction of boulders as he turns and runs. He hopes it will slow them down as he runs towards Hercules. &quot;Go! I'll catch up.&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#003366><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/ulionessofhera.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Lioness of Hera</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 17<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(7/9/01 11:35 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=110.topic&index=13>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> The Rockslide</span><hr size=1> The one lioness fell from Alastor's sword, her life gone as her sisters watched and roared in anger.  Sin struggled back up from being flung by Hercules and was a bit disoriented.  Then her eyes set up Alastor, she began to run after him, chasing him towards the mountain when the rockslide began.  <br>
Her gold eyes saw the limp form of the great Lion and she roared moving as fast as she could to save him.  Her sisters followed and they pulled him to safety.  <br>
Then Sin's eyes turned to Alastor and rushed after him.  As she pounced up the now loose rocks, they began to shift under her weight.  And began to tumble.  Sin, the lioness fell with them to the bottom.  A loud roar erupting from deep within her, and then she hit the ground. Laying still.  One of the sisters ran over to stand over Sin, eyeing the humans above.  The other two standing over the male.  They would not move, protecting their pride. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#336699><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uherculestlj.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Hercules TLJ</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Hero</span><br>  Posts: 100<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(7/9/01 2:38 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=110.topic&index=14>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Zeus's Temple</span><hr size=1> Hercules and Maia run to the temple and burst thru the doors.  He stops and looks back, still with his arm around Maia and catching his breath.  The priests and priestess's scurry around them offering them drinks and Hercules shakes his head.  His eyes stay in the door awaiting Alastor.  He isn't sure if he should go back and see if Alastor is okay. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#003366><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=alastorofancients>Alastor of Ancients</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 21<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(7/9/01 5:22 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=110.topic&index=15>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://caspervandien.net/sleepyhollow/themovie/photos/images/indeximageov.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Late arrival.</span><hr size=1> He stumbles in breathing heavily as he almost falls on the floor. His chest covered by stained crimson chainmail. He looks around with his blue eyes stepping inside.  He looks at Hercules and the woman as he slides the sword into the shealth on his back. He wiped back his now wet sweaty bangs looking towards them sighing. &quot;A rockslide stopped them. I don't know how long though. I'd get your father's attention some how. And if need be fortify this area.&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#336699><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uherculestlj.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Hercules TLJ</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Hero</span><br>  Posts: 101<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(7/9/01 5:51 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=110.topic&index=16>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Escape</span><hr size=1> As Herc watches Alastor and he begins to relax a bit and listens to him.  He glances out the doors that are still open.  &quot;No, we don't need Zeus's help,&quot; he says indignant. &quot;We can't stay here.  Besides, Maia's home is not far from here.  Once we get her there, she will be safe.  Hera and her minions cannot touch the there.&quot; Then he glances to the priests and priestess.  &quot;We need to  borrow your clothes,&quot; Herc gets them to exchange clothes with Alastor and Maia.  This way their scent would change a bit, and the lioness would be shaken off.<br>
He turns around and looks towards the back and then to Maia and Alastor.  &quot;Let's go out the back,&quot; he leads them out the back of the temple and into the woods. All they had to do was get to Mount Cyllene, Herc knew that.  All all would be alright.<br>
He lead them on at a rather fast pace, knowing to stop would surely allow the lioness to catch up.  <br>
After traveling for most of the day, the reach the bottom of the line of mountains that Mount Cyllene lies in. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#003366><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=alastorofancients>Alastor of Ancients</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 22<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(7/9/01 6:00 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=110.topic&index=17>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://caspervandien.net/sleepyhollow/themovie/photos/images/indeximageov.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Escape</span><hr size=1> He tugs at the clothes when he walks missing his armor. He looks around still having his pouch and sword, he would never give them up. He looked at Hercules as they walked deciding to try and strike up a conversation. He smiled remembering the little blonde man that was with him last they met. &quot;Where is Iolaus ?&quot; He tugged a slength of rope from his bag starting to braid it and tie 3 smooth round stones to the ends. He perked up his head ever careful as he started the process again tucking the finished ones into the pouch carefully placed not to tangle them.  <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=alastorofancients>Alastor of Ancients</A> at: 7/9/01 10:58:31 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#336699><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uherculestlj.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Hercules TLJ</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Hero</span><br>  Posts: 102<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(7/11/01 3:29 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=110.topic&index=18>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> the walk</span><hr size=1> Hercules glanced at Alastor, &quot;Iolaus? Well, he is probably wondering where I took off to.  This wasn't exactly a planned trip.&quot; He looked to Maia, &quot;But, when it comes to the Gods, you cannot always plan things.&quot;<br>
Soon, they began to walk up the Mount Cyllene.  It would take them a good while to reach the near top where Maia's cave sat. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#003366><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=alastorofancients>Alastor of Ancients</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 25<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(7/11/01 10:13 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=110.topic&index=19>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://caspervandien.net/sleepyhollow/themovie/photos/images/indeximageov.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Walking.</span><hr size=1> &quot;So how did you get involved in this?&quot; He walks up the side of the mountian. Pulling the robes up so he can walk without tripping. He looks down the rockside for movement. &quot;I think we lost the lions by the way.&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#336699><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/umaiathepleiade.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Maia the Pleiade</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 30<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(7/13/01 2:59 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=110.topic&index=20>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> home</span><hr size=1> As they begin the ascent up the mountain side, Maia begins to feel some relief.  For she is now home and safe.  She looks to the two as they chat about the rescue.  Winking at Hercules as he speaks that anything can happen when it comes to the Gods.<br>
&quot;Yes, and you did happen Hercules,&quot; she said softly. As Alastor spoke of the lions, Maia glanced back.  She knew they might have lost the lions, but she also knew Hera would be waiting for her to leave Mount Cyllene.  Maia began to move a bit quicker up the mountain as she saw the entrance to her cave.  She ran up ahead of the two and entered thru morning glory vines that partially covered the entrance.<br>
As she entered one would be very surprised at what they saw.  For inside it would seem they had entered a marble temple with great columns.  She breathed a sigh of relief and walked over to a pile of pillows and animal skins, falling into them and sitting there. <br>
&quot;please make yourselves at home, my heros!&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page  <b>1</b> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showMessageRange?topicID=110.topic&start=21&stop=27>2</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showPrevMessage?topicID=110.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showNextMessage?topicID=110.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=110.topic&index=20><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/blueMoon/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.emailToFriend?topicID=110.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.threadControl?topicID=110.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/blueMoon/deleteThread.jpg border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=110.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=110.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/unsubscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to stop receiving email notification of replies"> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies</a> <br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr al